<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.8.6">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2019-11-11T00:10:42+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/feed.xml</id><title type="html">HJ 기술 블로그 👨🏻‍💻</title><subtitle></subtitle><author><name>HyeongJu</name><email>hjkim880527@gmail.com</email></author><entry><title type="html">if __name__ ==’__main__’ 은 왜 사용할까?</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/2019-11-10/if-__name__-=='__main__'-%EC%9D%80-%EC%99%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0%EA%B9%8C" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="if __name__ =='__main__' 은 왜 사용할까?" /><published>2019-11-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2019-11-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/2019-11-10/if%20__name__%20=='__main__'%20%EC%9D%80%20%EC%99%9C%20%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0%EA%B9%8C</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/2019-11-10/if-__name__-=='__main__'-%EC%9D%80-%EC%99%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0%EA%B9%8C">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;name&lt;/strong&gt; 은 모듈의 이름을 저장하는 파이썬 내장 변수이다.&lt;br /&gt;
파이썬 파일은 두 가지 경우로 실행이 될 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.직접 실행하는 경우&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;__name__ 변수에 문자열 '__main__' 이 할당된다.  
함수가 아닌 0 deps의 코드를 실행.  
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2.import하는 경우&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;__name__ 변수에 해당 모듈의 이름이 할당.  
함수가 아닌 0 deps의 코드를 실행.  
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;name&lt;/strong&gt; 을 통해 파이썬 파일이 어떻게 실행되었는지를 알 수가 있다.&lt;br /&gt;
그리고 모듈을 import하면서 원치 않는 코드가 실행 될 수가 있다.&lt;br /&gt;
이것을 방지하기 위해 if &lt;strong&gt;name&lt;/strong&gt; == ‘&lt;strong&gt;main&lt;/strong&gt;’ 조건문을 통해 분기처리를 하는 것이다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ex) 예제 코드&lt;br /&gt;
1.print_hello.py를 직접 실행&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;print_hello.py&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;print_hello&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'hello'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'print_hello.py __name__:'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'test hello'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;실행결과&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;print_hello&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;py&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;__main__&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;hello&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;name&lt;/strong&gt; 이라는 변수에는 main 이 담겨져 있고, 0 deps 코드가 실행이 된다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.다른 파일에서 import&lt;br /&gt;
main.py&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kn&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nn&quot;&gt;print_hello&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'main.py __name__:'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;실행결과&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;print_hello.py __name__: hello
test hello
main.py __main__
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;name&lt;/strong&gt; 이라는 변수에는 print_hello 가 담겨지고, print_hello.py 를 import 하면서 0 deps 코드를 실행되었다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;정리&lt;br /&gt;
아래 처럼 조건을 통하여 원하는 분기처리를 하면된다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'__main__'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'직접 실행됨'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;'import되어 실행됨'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>HyeongJu</name></author><summary type="html">name 은 모듈의 이름을 저장하는 파이썬 내장 변수이다. 파이썬 파일은 두 가지 경우로 실행이 될 수 있다.</summary></entry></feed>